1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 15=

3
00:00:54,070 --> 00:00:54,910
(Huo Linchuan,)

4
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:57,790
(let me protect you this time.)

5
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,000
(I won't let anything happen to you.)

6
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,120
Did you sleep poorly last night?

7
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,430
You have dark circles under your eyes.

8
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:34,560
Maybe I was just too tired last night.

9
00:01:44,710 --> 00:01:45,550
Next time,

10
00:01:46,176 --> 00:01:47,296
I'll try to be more careful.

11
00:01:53,230 --> 00:01:55,280
Try to get some rest.

12
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,120
I'll come back later.

13
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,400
Alright.

14
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:22,560
(Lu Huaijin,)

15
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,710
(if it truly was you,)

16
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:26,800
(that grove...)

17
00:02:28,870 --> 00:02:30,520
Mr. Huo, this is the place.

18
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:33,470
We've been investigating in secret.

19
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,360
We found this area suspicious.

20
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,630
Search every corner.

21
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:48,460
(I'll use Huo Linchuan's name
to dismiss the guards.)

22
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:51,140
(Seize the chance
and kill your brother.)

23
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,840
(A letter addressed to Jiang Huaikang.)

24
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,120
(This handwriting
belongs to Lu Huaijin.)

25
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,750
(Just as I suspected.)

26
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,640
Mr. Huo.

27
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,190
Burn it.

28
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,030
Yes.

29
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,840
Mr. Huo.

30
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:52,710
Have you seen Ruoli?

31
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,560
No, I haven't.

32
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:55,870
Did you see Ruoli?

33
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,710
No, I didn't.

34
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,360
Ruoli.

35
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,680
Where is Ruoli?

36
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,150
She left early this morning
alone in the carriage,

37
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,710
heading toward the outskirts.

38
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,800
What?

39
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,200
And Lu Huaijin?

40
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:14,120
Mr. Lu left right after her, too,

41
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,720
also heading toward the outskirts.

42
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:19,560
Gather everyone at once.

43
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,270
Protect Ruoli at all costs.

44
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,430
Yes, Mr. Huo.

45
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,080
Lu Huaijin,

46
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,110
it really was you.

47
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,790
Ruoli,

48
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,070
why do you say that?

49
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,560
Controlling Jiang Huaikang,

50
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,040
killing my father,

51
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,560
framing Duke Huo...

52
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,400
Did you do

53
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,750
all these things?

54
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:00,470
Ruoli,

55
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,560
you truly are perceptive.

56
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,240
My father never wronged you.

57
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,360
Why did you do it?

58
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,463
Because if I killed him,

59
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,430
you'd have to seek my help.

60
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,310
After all, I grew up with you.

61
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,390
However,

62
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,600
you care about the title of the heir.

63
00:06:16,753 --> 00:06:17,879
Perhaps that's for the best.

64
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,680
You and Huo Linchuan got divorced

65
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,480
because of your father.

66
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,640
Shame on you.

67
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,360
I've never wanted to hurt you.

68
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,560
I just wanted to protect you,

69
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,950
just like when we were kids.

70
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,400
Protect me?

71
00:06:31,630 --> 00:06:33,000
You call this protection?

72
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,070
I've always guarded you so carefully.

73
00:06:37,126 --> 00:06:38,629
When Jiang Huaikang tried to kill you,

74
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,510
I struck him down

75
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,680
in a single blow.

76
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:43,160
I remember how you favored

77
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:44,909
the plum blossom hand warmer in winter.

78
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:48,950
I remember every callus on your hands
from practicing the qin.

79
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,630
I remember

80
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:51,990
you nearly drowned at age seven,

81
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,592
and you're afraid of the dark.

82
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,960
I remember everything about you

83
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:58,070
more clearly than Huo Linchuan does.

84
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:59,830
Why does he deserve your love?

85
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:00,670
Enough!

86
00:07:01,946 --> 00:07:03,750
It wasn't you who saved me
when I was little.

87
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:04,720
It was Huo Linchuan.

88
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,820
You've been lying to me all these years.

89
00:07:07,910 --> 00:07:08,750
Lu Huaijin,

90
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:10,160
you even fooled yourself.

91
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,720
Duke Huo treated you like his child,

92
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,160
raising you for so many years.

93
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:16,920
Huo Linchuan treated you like a brother.

94
00:07:17,670 --> 00:07:18,950
You repay kindness with betrayal.

95
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:20,630
You're nothing but heartless.

96
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,760
Jiang Ruoli,

97
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,190
you're far too naive.

98
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,800
Huo Wenyuan

99
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:31,830
adopted me

100
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:34,560
only to conceal the truth
from back then.

101
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:37,070
Everything Huo Linchuan has

102
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,120
should have belonged to me,

103
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,160
including you.

104
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,430
If he weren't the heir,

105
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:44,830
would you have married him?

106
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:48,560
Do you think everyone is
as depraved as you?

107
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,560
Depraved?

108
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,480
Everything I've done was for you.

109
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,686
Yet you want to save him?

110
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,120
He's been secretly investigating me.

111
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,190
Did you think I wouldn't notice?

112
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:06,160
If I have guessed correctly,

113
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,390
he's already on his way here,

114
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,750
about to fall right

115
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,040
into the trap I prepared for him.

116
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,560
Do it.

117
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,160
The Huo guards.

118
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,950
You keep surprising me,

119
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,950
but do you really think that's enough?

120
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:44,510
Leave no one alive.

121
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,480
Lu Huaijin,

122
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,600
it's time to put an end to this.

123
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:13,360
Jiang Ruoli, stop pushing me.

124
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:16,080
All I ever wanted was to be with you.

125
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:18,080
Why can't we be together?

126
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,920
Let go of me.

127
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:21,960
Lu Huaijin!

128
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,880
♪The dream shattered♪

129
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,920
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

130
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,560
♪Like a restless soul♪

131
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,000
♪How vague♪

132
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,920
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

133
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:02,160
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

134
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:05,560
♪Love and hate entwined♪

135
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,880
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

136
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:14,280
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

137
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,400
♪When fate falls apart♪

138
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:20,360
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

139
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,640
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

140
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:26,760
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

141
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:30,320
♪Life after life♪

142
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:33,480
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

143
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:38,200
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

144
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:41,320
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

145
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,880
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

146
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:46,000
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

147
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,520
♪Now shatter apart♪

148
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:51,400
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

149
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:54,920
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

150
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:58,040
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

151
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:02,760
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

152
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,920
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

153
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:10,480
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

154
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:16,400
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

155
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:19,560
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

156
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:22,520
♪Sober or indulge♪

157
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:28,960
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
